name: o11.1 — Mundanity — rev.10.1
description:
"The Coastline"

There is always an ocean next to you, and you have zero control over it. Enjoy it when the circumstances are benign, but be ready to find a shelter, when the weather changes.


/ Mundanity is a series of random thoughts of Trilo, reflecting on what is happening in physical or immaterial realms.
